{
  "texts": [
    "Finally, we successfully demonstrate that the LLMs capabilities can be improved by fine-tuning on teacher algorithm sequences.",
    "Limitations.",
    "We expect EvoLLM's performance to differ based on pretraining & fine-tuning protocols.",
    "Understanding how these details affect BBO performance is a key open challenge.",
    "Going forward LLMs capable of long context reasoning may be required to scale to larger search spaces."
  ]
}